And, you know, you explain, you can explain to people that involves,

00:12:35.280 --> 00:12:39.039
well, you, for observe, you give it an expression and that expression,

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:44.960
you know, we're not interested in the return value. We're only interested in the side effect

00:12:45.919 --> 00:12:51.679
that, of that, of that code. So, but still it's easy to forget that.

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:59.520
So in Python, we've used some different names. We've used, we used reactive calc

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:04.960
to represent the same thing as a reactive expression in R or this reactive

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:11.119
function name. And for observe, we're calling it a reactive effect. So, so this lets us use

